<concept id="concept_E8D43EB4494E41D2AB42D4A89396D1AB"
            xml:lang="en-us">
    <title>Installing the Log Agent</title>
    <conbody>
        <section>
            <p>For monitoring <ph conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"
                    />, a Log Agent must be installed on your <ph
                    conref="../../shared/product-name.xml#ProductNameTopic/Product_Abbr"/> host.</p>
            <p>As a prerequisite for installing the agent, the offline resources, the OpenStack extensions, and the Monitoring Service must have been installed.</p>
            <p>The installation consists of the following steps:</p>
            <ol>
                <li>Installing the agent.</li>
                <li>Configuring the agent.</li>
            </ol>
        </section>
    </conbody>
</concept>
